These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, soul, metal
3 different pets are kept: turtle, pony, goat
1. the fan of electronic is the owner of the pony##1
2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
4. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | metal | soul    |
| Pet     | pony    | goat       | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, chess
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, musical, satire
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person playing billiard is the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Game     | chess | backgammon | billiard  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary  | musical  | satire |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, bolivar, baccarat
There 3 different types of food: papaya, banana, grapefruit
1. the person eating banana is on the far left or far right##3
2. the cain-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is the person eating grapefruit##1
4. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Cigar           | baccarat | bolivar | cain |
| Food   | papaya        | grapefruit    | banana        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
City: marseilles, hannover, london
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, old-henry, davidoff
1. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
3. the swisher-smoker is between the person traveling to london and the davidoff-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| City   | london | hannover | marseilles |
| Cigar     | old-henry  | swisher    | davidoff  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
There 3 different types of food: radish, peas, apricot
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, juice
1. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating radish##1
4. the person eating radish is between the person eating peas and the person drinking juice##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Food   | peas | radish | apricot |
| Beverage     | fanta   | hot-chocolate   | juice   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
