2. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
4. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | gospel | house      |
| City     | liverpool  | rome | miami |

