2. the owner of the fish is in the middle##1
3. the dancer is on the left of the journalist##1
4. the journalist is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Job   | dancer        | journalist  | police-officer   |
| Pet       | cat | fish | hedgehog |

