.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-9::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, azalea, lily
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, taxi, ship
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
2. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who growslily##1
3. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3    |
| Flower           | marigold | azalea | lily |
| Transport   | ship    | car | taxi     |

