.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-10::.
3 different games are played: whist, scrabble, bridge
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, skiing, ice-hockey
1. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
3. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |
| Game      | whist | scrabble    | bridge      |
| Sport   | skiing       | biathlon | ice-hockey |

