2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person eating onion##1
3. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2       |       3        |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | martial-arts         | thriller          |
| Food        | onion | potato | cherry |

