.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-12::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, gardening, chess
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, classical, blues
1. the fan of metal is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
2. the fan of classical is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| Hobby      | gardening    | chess    | puzzles  |
| Music-Genre   | classical | metal | blues |

