2. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking water and the person drinking lemonade##2
4. the person drinking lemonade is the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
