2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the japanese##3
3. the japanese is the japanese##1
4. the american is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Pet   | chinchilla    | hamster   | rabbit |
| Nationality   | indian | japanese | american |

