.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-16::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile, helicopter
House: cottage, wooden, art-deco
1. the wooden house is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is between the art-deco house and the cottage house##2
3. the wooden house is on the right of the cottage house##1
4. the art-deco house is the person driving the scooter##1
5. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |     3     |
| Transport   | snowmobile | helicopter | scooter |
| House   | cottage     | wooden  | art-deco    |

