.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-19::.
House: modern, ranch-style, colonial
3 different games are played: billiard, domino, monopoly
1. the modern house is the person playing billiard##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
3. the person playing domino is in the middle##1
4. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |
