.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, video-games, gardening
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, chinchilla, frog
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Hobby      | gardening    | video-games | collecting         |
| Pet   | frog | chinchilla  | goldfish |

 